Step 1: Get Docker container running to provide you your Python Learning environment on the go (Command something similar to the below one)
sudo docker run --name mypythonbox -v /home/kd/PythonTheHardWay/Programming:/data -P -d kuldeeparyadotcom/learnpython

Step 2: SSH to your container (Command something similar to the below one)
ssh admin@DockerTutorialsAdvanced -p 49156

Enjoy!

